{"type":null,"faqId":46187,"title":"为什么屏幕亮度偏暗或者偏亮？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:微软雅黑;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、请确认光感应器是否正常。光感应器被异物遮挡可能引起屏幕亮度异常。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、华为手机默认打开的是自动亮度调节功能，会依据环境光亮度，自动调节背光亮度，增加您视觉上的舒适度。如果您不满意，可以关闭自动亮度调节功能，自行调节背光亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果感觉屏幕偏亮或偏暗，请调整屏幕亮度。点击设置-显示-亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、请确认是否进入超级省电模式。超级省电模式下，屏幕会变暗，且只能使用电话、信息和联系人功能。点击退出按钮即可退出超级省电模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、</span><span class=\"s1\">如果屏幕曾受到外部冲击，内部液晶可能会破损并导致屏幕亮度或色彩异常。请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1967","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376337000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":16,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"屏幕,亮度,偏亮,偏暗","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}